TITLE: Initializing Scatter Chart with Chart.js
DESCRIPTION: Creates a basic scatter chart with 4 data points using Chart.js. The example demonstrates setting up the data structure, configuring chart options, and defining the scatter plot type with a linear x-axis.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/blob/master/docs/charts/scatter.md#2025-04-08_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// <block:setup:1>
const data = {
  datasets: [{
    label: 'Scatter Dataset',
    data: [{
      x: -10,
      y: 0
    }, {
      x: 0,
      y: 10
    }, {
      x: 10,
      y: 5
    }, {
      x: 0.5,
      y: 5.5
    }],
    backgroundColor: 'rgb(255, 99, 132)'
