DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use animation callbacks in Chart.js to track animation progress. It demonstrates updating a progress bar during chart animation by using the onProgress callback.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/blob/master/docs/configuration/animations.md#2025-04-08_snippet_2

