TITLE: Creating a Basic Mixed Chart with Bar and Line Datasets in Chart.js
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a mixed chart combining bar and line chart types by specifying the chart type on each dataset. The example shows a bar dataset and a line dataset sharing the same labels.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/blob/master/docs/charts/mixed.md#2025-04-08_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const mixedChart = new Chart(ctx, {
    data: {
        datasets: [{
            type: 'bar',
            label: 'Bar Dataset',
            data: [10, 20, 30, 40]
        }, {
            type: 'line',
            label: 'Line Dataset',
            data: [50, 50, 50, 50],
        }],
        labels: ['January', 'February', 'March', 'April']
    },
    options: options
});
```

