TITLE: Defining Common Cartesian Axis Options in Chart.js
DESCRIPTION: This markdown table defines common configuration options for cartesian axes in Chart.js. It specifies the namespace and lists various properties with their types, default values, and descriptions. The options cover aspects like scale bounds, clipping, axis positioning, stacking, and scale titling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/blob/master/docs/axes/cartesian/_common.md#2025-04-08_snippet_0

