TITLE: Grid Line Configuration Options Table in Chart.js
DESCRIPTION: Markdown table defining configuration options for grid lines in Chart.js axes. Includes properties like circular, color, display, and various styling options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chartjs/Chart.js/blob/master/docs/axes/styling.md#2025-04-08_snippet_0

